overview.en: MFA is a decentralized film industry chain, by Dr Zheng Ming tower and Dr Jian-rong zheng founded in Singapore, MFA film industry and chain has a large capacity of transmission speed, trading, resistance to attack the distinctive features of quantum, block chain and chain is the third generation leaders.
overview.zh: MFA是一条去中心化的电影行业公链，由郑座明博士和郑建荣博士在新加坡创立，MFA电影行业公链具有传输速度快、交易容量大、抗量子攻击的显著特点，是第三代区块链公链的领导者。
